---
title: Crispy Shallot Pork Croquettes with Gravy, Mash and Parmesan Green Beans
description: Pork and potato patties are encrusted with a crushed buttery panko and crispy shallot coating before baking, for a simple meal with complex flavours. Mash smothered in a velvety gravy with parmesan green beans rounds out the dish with lovely textures and bold taste!
